{"layout":"logicalStructure","root":{"data":{"text":"<p>MySQL 中的事务隔离级别有哪些</p>","uid":"99b7a8eb-c2a9-4af0-a6a1-6102abb5fd7b","generalization":[],"expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"imgMap":{}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>读未提交(READ UNCOMMITTED)</p>","uid":"3a6efde7-ecfd-4fb9-8377-b14a939a06ff","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>一个事务可以看到另一个事务未提交提交的数据修改</p>","uid":"5c3535c2-678d-4982-a97b-56b6541cae17","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>存在脏读问题</p>","uid":"1cae4e37-5fb3-41bf-9593-d1a48750f1aa","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>读已提交(READCOMMITTED)</p>","uid":"5c5fadc8-4d94-4f44-9323-ba541c888356","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>一个事务只能看到已经提交事务的数据</p>","uid":"3e701dbf-5323-44e8-a58b-4927ffba93fa","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>防止脏读，存在不可重复读</p>","uid":"9648ff30-408f-4280-af31-6b97779b4268","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"note":"不可重复读就是同一事务里，多次读同一数据，结果却不一样，因为其他已提交事务中途改了数据。\n\n简单举例：  \n- 事务A：第一次读“用户余额=100” → 未提交  \n- 事务B：修改该用户余额为200 → 提交  \n- 事务A：第二次读“用户余额”，若出现“不可重复读”，结果会变成200（与第一次不一致）；若处于“可重复读”隔离级，结果仍为100。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>可重复读(REPEATABLE READ)</p>","uid":"9a69e771-20bb-4bc2-8549-31459bdac387","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>确保在一个事务中的多个查询返回的结果是一致的</p>","uid":"d98b0023-0705-4577-9370-95cf8dfa8ec0","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>避免不可重复读问题，但是可能会引发幻读问题</p>","uid":"21d4263b-ebcb-472f-97bf-9483c3d96c85","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"在同一事务中，对相同查询条件执行多次读取操作，即使每次读取前都没有修改过数据，最终得到的数据行数量或行本身却不一致。\n\n简单举例：  \n- 事务A：第一次执行查询 `SELECT * FROM 用户 WHERE 余额 < 200`，此时查询到有1条记录（用户A，余额100）→ 未提交。\n- 事务B：插入一条新记录（用户B，余额150），并提交事务。\n- 事务A：第二次执行相同的查询 `SELECT * FROM 用户 WHERE 余额 < 200`，若出现“幻读”，会查询到2条记录（用户A和用户B），与第一次查询结果的行数不一致；"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>串行化(SERIALIZABLE)</p>","uid":"8c3f8780-703d-41c3-91cb-e420266c6170","generalization":[],"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>执行被保证是可串行化</p>","uid":"12e02b3f-edc5-4620-9a24-83518552a7c6","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p>这可以避免所有的并发问题，但是会大大降低并发性能。</p>","uid":"3c894d87-e1d6-444c-aa38-977290d7cd0b","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]}],"smmVersion":"0.14.0-fix.1"},"theme":{"template":"coffee","config":{}},"view":{"transform":{"scaleX":1.2,"scaleY":1.2,"shear":0,"rotate":0,"translateX":-994.5428571428572,"translateY":-159.4285714285715,"originX":0,"originY":0,"a":1.2,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1.2,"e":-994.5428571428572,"f":-159.4285714285715},"state":{"scale":1.2,"x":-994.5428571428572,"y":-159.4285714285715,"sx":-994.5428571428572,"sy":-159.4285714285715}}}